{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "d0e1f203-1a2f-082d-72a2-b28100818b9c",
    "name": "Employee Management API",
    "description": "Complete collection for Employee Management System APIs with JWT Authentication.\n\n🔐 AUTHENTICATION:\n- Register users (automatically creates employee profile)\n- Login to get JWT token\n- Refresh token to extend session\n- Logout to invalidate refresh token\n- Use Bearer token for secured endpoints\n\n📱 REGISTRATION REQUIREMENTS:\n- Name: Minimum 3 characters\n- Email: Valid email format\n- Password: Minimum 6 characters\n- Phone Number: Exactly 10 digits (optional)\n- Role: SYSTEM_ADMIN, USER_ADMIN, or EMPLOYEE_VIEWER\n\n👤 EMPLOYEE MANAGEMENT:\n- Paginated employee listing\n- Get own profile (/me)\n- CRUD operations with role-based access\n- Restore soft-deleted employees\n- Search employees by name or department\n- Upload profile images (stores file ID)\n- SYSTEM_ADMIN: Full access\n- USER_ADMIN: Create, Update, View access\n- EMPLOYEE_VIEWER: Read access + own profile management\n\n📝 CREATE EMPLOYEE REQUIREMENTS:\n- firstName: Required, string\n- lastName: Optional, string\n- email: Required, valid email format\n- department: Required, string (department name)\n- salary: Required, positive number\n\n🏢 DEPARTMENT MANAGEMENT:\n- Create, Read, Update departments\n- Assign employees to departments\n\n📁 FILE MANAGEMENT:\n- Upload profile images for users\n- Get all files metadata\n- Download specific files\n\n🌐 PUBLIC ENDPOINTS:\n- Health check (/api/public/health)\n- API information (/api/public/info)\n\n📧 FEATURES:\n- Async welcome email sending\n- Duplicate prevention (email & phone)\n- Input validation\n- Comprehensive error handling\n- File upload with automatic profile linking",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🌐 Public",
      "description": "Public endpoints that don't require authentication.",
